vote.title: An ordinance granting a private license to Donald James McNamara, Jr. and Joan P. McNamara, for the use of approximately 204 square feet of land to install, occupy, maintain and utilize a barrier wall on a portion of Overbrook Drive right-of-way located near its intersection with Abbott Avenue - Revenue: General Fund $2,497.00, plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
